Text: LEADS LEADS LEADSPST HOW MANY LEADS DO YOU NEED TODAY If you are trying to sell a product or service on the Net A steady stream of qualified LEADS is one of the most important ingredients in building a successful business Read On if you are interested in Expanding your Business Increasing your Sales Maximizing your Profits Direct Email Marketing is the most costeffective way to generate large amounts of fresh hot leads Let us help you develop and manage a high response list of prospects that indicate an interest in receiving information about your products or services We are Contract Mailers who send to Quality Lists that have been cleaned and verified Contract Mailing We can send your ad to or to million We honor all remove requests so you dont get the flames You Get Only the Qualified Leads sent to your web site the ones that have optedin to receive your information ALL The Leads You Need No More SPAM Complaints To find out how to get the leads that you NEED Dont waste another minute To Optin to receive more info hit REPLY and type LEADS in the SUBJECT Box YOU MUST INCLUDE YOUR NAME AND PHONE NUMBER TO RECEIVE A RESPONSE TO THIS OFFER To permanently remove yourself from our mailing list click reply and type REMOVE in the SUBJECT Box IMPORTANT It is our intention to honor ALL Remove Requests However If you do not type REMOVE in the SUBJECT Box our software cannot read it you WILL NOT be removed BR This message is in full compliance with US Federal requirements for commercial email under bill S Title lll Section Paragraph aC passed by the th US Congress and cannot be considered SPAM since it includes a remove mechanism
